dct_title_s: Map of the glacial geology of the Catskill Mountains
dct_description_sm: Companion text: Glacial geology of the Catskills / John Lyon Rich. New York. State Museum. Bulletin 299; 1935. 180p. 1 pl. Relief shown by form lines. Map is plate 1 accompanied by plate 2: Map of the Catskill Mountain region showing positions of the ice front during the glacial retreat.
dct_publisher_sm: Albany, N.Y. : University of the State of New York, New York State Museum, 1930.
